The older main gun for small vessels.<br/>Equipped as the standard weapon on old destroyers.<br/>Both loading and rotation were hand-operated, but with its simple construction and low cost, it served for a long time as the main weapon of destroyers and escorts.<br/>Not intended for anti-air firing.

